@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) of US009 - Schedule a visit

autonumber

actor "Client" as Client
participant ":System" as System

activate Client

    Client -> System : Asks to list of available properties (devo comeÃ§ar por aqui ou logo no pedido de agendamento?)
        activate System

        System --> Client : Displays the list of announcements and a menu where you can Schedule a visit
    deactivate System

    Client -> System : Selects the option to schedule a visit
        activate System

    loop    [Schedule_visit]
        System --> Client : Ask to select the announcement ID to schedule a visit
    deactivate System

    Client -> System : Types the announcement ID
        activate System

        System --> Client : Requests data (date of visit, time of visit start and time of visit end))
    deactivate System

    Client -> System : Types requested data (date of visit, time of visit start and time of visit end)
        activate System

        System --> Client : Confirm there is not a visit request from the same client at the same time and display the data \ntyped by the client for confirmation
    deactivate System

    Client -> System : Confirms the information is correct and asks to send the message to the agent
        activate System

        System --> Client : Send the message to the agent and show a confirmation message to the client
    deactivate System
    end


@enduml